Class ClassToRuleBodyConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.rulewerk.owlapi.AbstractClassToRuleConverter
      • org.semanticweb.rulewerk.owlapi.ClassToRuleBodyConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLClassExpressionVisitor, org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLClassVisitorBase, org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLVisitorBase
    public class ClassToRuleBodyConverter
extends AbstractClassToRuleConverter
implements org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLClassExpressionVisitor
    Helper class for transforming OWL class expressions that occur as subclasses into suitable body literals for rules. Auxiliary rules might be created to capture the semantics of some constructs.
